   - **Use Anti-CSRF Libraries**: Implement libraries such as **OWASP CSRFGuard** to help prevent CSRF attacks.
   - **Double-Submitted Cookie Method**: Generate a pseudorandom value and set it as a cookie. Require this value to be included in every form submission.
